  "text": "Our analysis was completed in four stages and was derived from [CITATION_1] phase strategy for explicating data. In the first stage of our analysis, we used the following questions to identify 'units of meaning' that could be used in constructing teacher orientation profiles at the beginning and conclusions of a year of PD:",
